title: Music Therapy [Online]
description: WC Partners has partnered with the Center for Music Therapy and Wellness to bring music therapy classes to Marshfield. Once a week, practitioners from the Center for Music Therapy and Wellness come and engage with individuals we serve to promote communication and interaction through music therapy.

title: Virtual Halloween Bingo [Online]
description: WC Partners is hosting a Virtual Halloween Bingo! Dress up as your favorite or spookiest Halloween character for a virtual meetup where we will play bingo and there will be prizes. The meetup will be hosted online using Microsoft Teams (no account signup is necessary).
